mages\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"sales\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1323}, {\"ngram\": \"a notable 23 per cent increase\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"key victories\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay in the game with The Turnover: your weekly roundup of sport business news, expert analysis and behind\\u2011the\\u2011scenes stories from City AM's sports desk.\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1452}, {\"ngram\": \"The Turnover\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1470}, {\"ngram\": \"your weekly roundup\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1491}, {\"ngram\": \"sport business news\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1514}, {\"ngram\": \"analysis and behind\\u2011the\\u2011scenes stories\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1561}, {\"ngram\": \"City AM's sports desk\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The campaign's success underscored the power of integrating product placement with real-time social media amplification, setting a new benchmark for how to activate Olympic sponsorship rights.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The campaign's success\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1613}, {\"ngram\": \"the power\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1635}, {\"ngram\": \"product placement\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 1668}, {\"ngram\": \"real-time social media amplification\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1710}, {\"ngram\": \"a new benchmark\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1735}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic sponsorship rights\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Relaxed IOC rules at Paris 2024 also allowed for more direct, unfiltered athlete-to-fan interactions - a move that brands were quick to leverage.\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1930, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Relaxed IOC rules\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1802}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1811}, {\"ngram\": \"fan\", \"from\": 